# Backend ORIGIN the device/emulator can actually reach (plan §M.8, §8.4).
# `homeops.localhost` does NOT resolve from a device — use the host LAN IP or an HTTPS
# tunnel, and trust the mkcert root CA on the device. Set the origin only (no `/api`);
# `src/lib/api.ts` appends the `/api` prefix. Example:
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE=https://192.168.1.10
